Class-StateMachine-Declarative
==============================

Build state machine classes declaratively

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Class::StateMachine

